      <title>美国称中国针对关键基础设施的黑客活动可追溯到五年前</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-hacking-campaign-aimed-critical-infrastructure-goes-back-five-years-us-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和盟国情报机构周三在一份联合声明中表示，一个针对美国关键基础设施的先进中国黑客组织已经活跃了五年之久。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-hacking-campaign-aimed-critical-infrastructure-goes-back-five-years-us-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 16:45:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国尹在妻子“迪奥包丑闻”后誓言制定更明确的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-vows-clearer-rules-after-wifes-dior-bag-scandal-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈周三表示，韩国第一夫人接受迪奥包包作为礼物的隐藏摄像机镜头的发布是一种“政治策略”，但他誓言要划定更明确的界限，以确保此类事件不再发生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-vows-clearer-rules-after-wifes-dior-bag-scandal-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:51:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国因火灾风险终止对 300 万辆现代起亚汽车的调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-closes-probe-into-3-mln-hyundai-kia-vehicles-over-fire-risks-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国汽车安全监管机构周三表示，他们已结束对 300 万辆现代汽车和起亚汽车发动机起火风险的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-closes-probe-into-3-mln-hyundai-kia-vehicles-over-fire-risks-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部融资报告发现美国面临来自俄罗斯、朝鲜的更大风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-faces-heightened-risk-russia-north-korea-treasury-financing-report-finds-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部在周三发布的新的洗钱、恐怖主义融资和扩散融资国家风险评估中表示，美国面临来自俄罗斯的更大风险，俄罗斯正试图获取具有军事用途的商品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-faces-heightened-risk-russia-north-korea-treasury-financing-report-finds-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国不会再接纳更多罗辛亚难民——部长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bangladesh-will-not-let-any-more-rohingya-refugees-minister-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国周三表示，将不再允许更多来自缅甸的罗兴亚难民进入该国，因为支持已经存在的大量罗兴亚难民会威胁到其自身安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bangladesh-will-not-let-any-more-rohingya-refugees-minister-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:49:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年巴基斯坦选举：谁是总统候选人？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/who-are-key-players-pakistans-general-elections-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦周四举行全国选举，该国正努力应对 2022 年前总理伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 下台后的经济危机和政治不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/who-are-key-players-pakistans-general-elections-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:26:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年巴基斯坦大选：海报占据主导地位，卡车上的艺术品逐渐减少</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-political-art-trucks-hurt-by-preference-posters-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[选举前曾经在巴基斯坦道路和高速公路上点缀着政治领导人画作的彩色卡车在这个投票季消失了，取而代之的是海报和横幅上的印刷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-political-art-trucks-hurt-by-preference-posters-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国政府上任以来首次与叛乱分子举行和谈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-govt-holds-first-peace-talks-with-insurgents-since-taking-office-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与会者周三表示，泰国政府自去年上任以来首次恢复与南部叛乱分子的谈判，双方同意进一步讨论该地区和平路线图草案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-govt-holds-first-peace-talks-with-insurgents-since-taking-office-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：上海将允许外国公司更快地从中国传输数据-消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-allow-faster-data-transfer-china-foreign-firms-sources-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四位知情人士表示，上海计划加快对希望将本地数据发送到海外的外国公司的审批，这将是中国一年多前公布的严格数据规则的重大放松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-allow-faster-data-transfer-china-foreign-firms-sources-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:36:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾因旅游业和航线争端而停止新的中国团体旅行</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-stops-new-group-trips-china-amid-tourism-air-route-spat-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾周三告诉其旅行社停止组织新的前往中国的团体旅游，因为北京尚未允许中国游客前往台湾进行此类旅行，并且已经改变了敏感的台湾海峡的飞行路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-stops-new-group-trips-china-amid-tourism-air-route-spat-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
